data.description: This beautiful, well cared for 2 bed 1 bath home is ready for a new family! This home offers an overall cozy feel, with a comfortable living room, spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a nice sized bathroom. There is an inside laundry room with additional storage space as well. The front of the home has a large florida room, perfect for relaxing. The generous sized yard is great for entertaining or enjoy your evenings.  This home has a new range and range hood (2023) in the kitchen, new water softener (2023), new a/c (2023), and newer roof (2018).  This home is conveniently located near, Gemini Springs and Blue Springs State Parks that have walking and biking trails, the Sun Rail Train, the St. Johns River, schools, shopping, I-4 and medical.  It's also centrally located between Daytona Beach and Orlando! Schedule your showing today before this gem is sold!
